Saya sudah menelepon ambulans.

00:19:52.800 --> 00:19:54.240
Mereka akan berada di sini sebentar lagi.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:12.800
Tuan Shiv Kashyap?

00:20:20.440 --> 00:20:21.800
Tuan Shiv Kashyap?

